# .gitignore — plaintext-labs
# These labs run tools (tcpdump, openssl, volatility, metasploit, prowler, …) that emit
# captures, keys, dumps and logs. Small curated seed data under data/ is committed on
# purpose; the heavy/dangerous artifacts below never are — labs download or generate them.

# === Secrets — never commit ===
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
*_rsa
*_dsa
*_ed25519
*.kdbx
*.token
credentials

# === Generated lab artifacts: captures, memory/disk images, logs ===
*.pcap
*.pcapng
*.cap
*.log
*.dmp
*.mem
*.vmem
*.raw
*.lime
*.E01
*.aff4

# === Malware samples — keep out of the repo entirely ===
samples/
*.malware

# === Python tooling ===
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
venv/

# === OS / editor cruft ===
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
